---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="服務項目"
    description="專業的數據中心與企業機房解決方案"
    lang="zh-TW"
>
    <section class="services-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
            T-Vetas Network 以高品質、適用且具成本效益的工程服務和最佳解決方案聞名，豐富的專案經驗讓我們在業界處於領先地位。
        </p>

        <div class="services-grid">
            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>工程施工</h3>
                <p class="card-description">為客戶提供電信機房/資料中心所需的設計/安裝等電信服務</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>EHS (環境、健康與安全管理)</li>
                    <li>BIM/CAD 工程設計與建模</li>
                    <li>數據中心建置</li>
                    <li>電力系統規劃與施工</li>
                    <li>結構化佈線系統施工</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>物料供應</h3>
                <p class="card-description">為客戶提供所需的施工物料，合作夥伴包含：</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>CORNING (康寧)</li>
                    <li>Ciena</li>
                    <li>Infinera</li>
                    <li>Schneider (施耐德), APC</li>
                    <li>Panduit</li>
                    <li>AFL</li>
                    <li>JPC</li>
                    <li>Dell</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>證書</h3>
                <p class="card-description">證書是展現一個公司安裝/測試人員的品質的方法, 我們公司擁有許多跨國公司的認證</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>CORNING (康寧)</li>
                    <li>Ciena</li>
                    <li>Infinera</li>
                    <li>Panduit</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>網路解決方案</h3>
                <p class="card-description">我們針對客戶的需求提供不同的網路解決方案</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>IP network</li>
                    <li>SDH/WDM network</li>
                    <li>Wifi network</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="service-card">
                <h3>維護</h3>
                <p class="card-description">我們為許多企業提供智慧手服務，確保客戶的服務全年365天正常運作</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>XXXX Smarthand</li>
                    <li>XXXXXXXXX smarthand</li>
                    <li>XXXXXX smarthand</li>
                    <li>XXXXXXX Smarthand</li>
                    <li>XXXX smarthand</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.services-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
}

.section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    color: #1A2A47;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.section-description {
    text-align: center;
    color: #4a5568;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5rem;
}

.service-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1A2A47;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.service-card ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: #4a5568;
}

.service-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.full-width {
    grid-column: span 2;
}

.highlight-text {
    color: #4a5568;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.card-description {
    color: #4a5568;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .full-width {
        grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .services-container {
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }
}
</style>